        public boolean isConstraintMatchEnabled()
        Description copied from interface: ScoreHolder
        Must be in sync with ScoreDirector.isConstraintMatchEnabled() for the ScoreDirector which contains this ScoreHolder.

        Defaults to true.

        Specified by:
